          <small>${escapeHtml(latest.title || "Preparing")}${latest.detail ? ` ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â· ${escapeHtml(latest.detail)}` : ""}</small>
